import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='home_score', bins=10, kde=True)
    plt.axvline(data['home_score'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['home_score'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the distribution of home scores?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='away_score', bins=10, kde=True)
    median_away_score = data['away_score'].median()
    plt.axvline(median_away_score, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Median: {median_away_score:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of away scores?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='score_difference', bins=18, kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['score_difference'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['score_difference'].median():.2f}")
    plt.title("What is the distribution of score difference?", wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby('home_team')['home_score'].mean().sort_values(ascending=False).reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='home_team', y='home_score', data=data_grouped)
    plt.title('Which teams have the highest average home scores?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.xlabel('Home Team')
    plt.ylabel('Average Home Score')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):

    data = data.sort_values('away_score', ascending=False)
    chart = sns.barplot(x='away_team', y='away_score', data=data)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.title('Which teams have the highest average away scores?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
